975
01:19:37,065 --> 01:19:39,216
<font color="#ffff80">[100 Days My Prince]</font>

976
01:19:39,735 --> 01:19:42,164
<font color="#ffff80">Jika aku harus meletakkan pisau di lehernya,</font>

977
01:19:42,165 --> 01:19:43,992
<font color="#ffff80">Aku akan melakukannya sendiri.</font>

978
01:19:44,105 --> 01:19:47,508
<font color="#ffff80">Apa kau yang mencoba membunuh Putra Mahkota?</font>

979
01:19:48,275 --> 01:19:50,496
<font color="#ffff80">Yoon Yi Suh.</font>

980
01:19:50,674 --> 01:19:54,685
<font color="#ffff80">Gadis itu ada di genggamanku.</font>

981
01:19:55,445 --> 01:19:56,667
<font color="#ffff80">Aku akan...</font>

982
01:19:58,815 --> 01:20:00,502
<font color="#ffff80">...menikahimu.</font>

983
01:20:00,955 --> 01:20:04,429
<font color="#ffff80">Jangan khawatir. Aku akan menemukanmu.</font>

984
01:20:07,424 --> 01:20:08,474
<font color="#ffff80">Aku...</font>

985
01:20:09,365 --> 01:20:10,980
<font color="#ffff80">...menjemput ajalku.</font>

